    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="哈希表-Hash"><a href="#哈希表-Hash" class="headerlink" title="哈希表(Hash)"></a>哈希表(Hash)</h1><p><strong>哈希表</strong>：是根据关键字而直接进行访问的数据结构。也就是说，哈希表建立了关键字和存储地址之间的一种直接映射关系。  </p><p><strong>哈希的基本原理</strong>：是将给定的键值转换为偏移地址来检索记录。<br>键转换为地址是通过一种关系(公式)来完成的，这就是哈希（散列）函数。Hash(key)=Addr。（这里的地址可以是数组下标、索引。或内存地址等。） </p><p><strong>缺点</strong>：两个不同的关键字，由于哈希函数值相同，因而被映射到同一表位置上。该现象称为冲突。发生冲突的两个关键字称为该哈希函数的同义词。</p><a id="more"></a><img src="/2020/11/19/%E5%93%88%E5%B8%8C%E8%A1%A8%E6%80%BB%E7%BB%93/hash.png" alt="hash" style="zoom:50%;"><p>本文主要总结了LeetCode上哈希表相关的题目，会持续更新~</p><h1 id="题目列表"><a href="#题目列表" class="headerlink" title="题目列表"></a>题目列表</h1><table><thead><tr><th>#</th><th>Title</th><th>Remark</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>1</td><td>两数之和</td><td>Easy</td></tr><tr><td>380</td><td>常数时间插入、删除和获取随机元素</td><td>Medium</td></tr><tr><td>771</td><td>宝石和石头</td><td>Easy</td></tr></tbody></table><h1 id="例1"><a href="#例1" class="headerlink" title="例1"></a>例1</h1><h2 id="1-两数之和"><a href="#1-两数之和" class="headerlink" title="1.两数之和"></a>1.两数之和</h2><h2 id="题目地址"><a href="#题目地址" class="headerlink" title="题目地址"></a>题目地址</h2><p><a href="https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/two-sum">https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/two-sum</a></p><h2 id="题目描述"><a href="#题目描述" class="headerlink" title="题目描述"></a>题目描述</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">给定一个整数数组 nums 和一个目标值 target，请你在该数组中找出和为目标值的那 两个 整数，并返回他们的数组下标。</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">你可以假设每种输入只会对应一个答案。但是，你不能重复利用这个数组中同样的元素。</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">示例:</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">给定 nums &#x3D; [2, 7, 11, 15], target &#x3D; 9</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">因为 nums[0] + nums[1] &#x3D; 2 + 7 &#x3D; 9</span><br><span class="line">所以返回 [0, 1]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="思路"><a href="#思路" class="headerlink" title="思路"></a>思路</h2><p>使用一个map记录已经遍历过的数字及其对应的索引值。对于每一次遍历：</p><p>1、去map中查询target-nums[i]是否存在</p><p>2、如果存在，则条件成立，返回</p><p>3、如果不存在，则将当前数字存如map中，值作为key,下标作为value。</p><h2 id="代码"><a href="#代码" class="headerlink" title="代码"></a>代码</h2><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">var</span> twoSum=<span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span>(<span class="params">nums,target</span>)</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">const</span> map=<span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="built_in">Map</span>();</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="title">for</span>(<span class="params"><span class="keyword">let</span> i=<span class="number">0</span>;i&lt;nums.length;i++</span>)</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">const</span> diff=target-nums[i];</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="function"><span class="title">if</span>(<span class="params">map.has(diff)</span>)</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">return</span> [map.get(diff),i]</span><br><span class="line">           &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        map.set(nums[i],i);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="复杂度分析"><a href="#复杂度分析" class="headerlink" title="复杂度分析"></a>复杂度分析</h2><p>时间复杂度：O(N)<br>空间复杂度：O(N)</p><h1 id="例2"><a href="#例2" class="headerlink" title="例2"></a>例2</h1><h2 id="380-常数时间插入、删除和获取随机元素"><a href="#380-常数时间插入、删除和获取随机元素" class="headerlink" title="380.常数时间插入、删除和获取随机元素"></a>380.常数时间插入、删除和获取随机元素</h2><h2 id="题目地址-1"><a href="#题目地址-1" class="headerlink" title="题目地址"></a>题目地址</h2><p><a href="https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/insert-delete-getrandom-o1/">https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/insert-delete-getrandom-o1/</a></p><h2 id="题目描述-1"><a href="#题目描述-1" class="headerlink" title="题目描述"></a>题目描述</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">设计一个支持在平均 时间复杂度 O(1) 下，执行以下操作的数据结构。</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">insert(val)：当元素 val 不存在时，向集合中插入该项。</span><br><span class="line">remove(val)：元素 val 存在时，从集合中移除该项。</span><br><span class="line">getRandom：随机返回现有集合中的一项。每个元素应该有相同的概率被返回。</span><br><span class="line">示例 :</span><br><span class="line">&#x2F;&#x2F; 初始化一个空的集合。</span><br><span class="line">RandomizedSet randomSet &#x3D; new RandomizedSet();</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#x2F;&#x2F; 向集合中插入 1 。返回 true 表示 1 被成功地插入。</span><br><span class="line">randomSet.insert(1);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#x2F;&#x2F; 返回 false ，表示集合中不存在 2 。</span><br><span class="line">randomSet.remove(2);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#x2F;&#x2F; 向集合中插入 2 。返回 true 。集合现在包含 [1,2] 。</span><br><span class="line">randomSet.insert(2);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#x2F;&#x2F; getRandom 应随机返回 1 或 2 。</span><br><span class="line">randomSet.getRandom();</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#x2F;&#x2F; 从集合中移除 1 ，返回 true 。集合现在包含 [2] 。</span><br><span class="line">randomSet.remove(1);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#x2F;&#x2F; 2 已在集合中，所以返回 false 。</span><br><span class="line">randomSet.insert(2);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#x2F;&#x2F; 由于 2 是集合中唯一的数字，getRandom 总是返回 2 。</span><br><span class="line">randomSet.getRandom();</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="思路-1"><a href="#思路-1" class="headerlink" title="思路"></a>思路</h2><p>1、要求平均时间复杂度为O(1)，这道题的核心是考察基本数据结构和算法的操作及其时间复杂度。</p><p>2、回顾一下基础知识：几种数据结构的查找、删除、插入的时间复杂度。  </p><table><thead><tr><th>数据结构</th><th>查找</th><th>插入</th><th>删除</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>数组</td><td>值O(N)索引O(1)</td><td>O(1)</td><td>O(N)</td></tr><tr><td>有序数组</td><td>O(logN)</td><td>O(N)</td><td>O(N)</td></tr><tr><td>链表</td><td>O(N)</td><td>O(1)</td><td>O(N)</td></tr><tr><td>有序链表</td><td>O(N)</td><td>O(N)</td><td>O(N)</td></tr><tr><td>哈希表</td><td>O(N)(正常情况下)</td><td>O(1)</td><td>O(1)</td></tr></tbody></table><p>3、所以要考虑使用多种数据结构来实现，使用以下数据结构：<br>动态数组存储元素值<br>哈希表存储值到索引的映射</p><p>4、对于删除，使用一些技巧。<br>将要删除的元素和最后一个元素交换。<br>将最后一个元素删除</p><h2 id="代码-1"><a href="#代码-1" class="headerlink" title="代码"></a>代码</h2><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">var</span> RandomizedSet = <span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span>(<span class="params"></span>) </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">this</span>.map = <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="built_in">Map</span>();</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">this</span>.values = [];</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br><span class="line">RandomizedSet.prototype.insert = <span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span>(<span class="params">val</span>)</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> (<span class="built_in">this</span>.map.has(val)) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="literal">false</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">this</span>.map.set(val,<span class="built_in">this</span>.values.length);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">this</span>.values.push(val);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="literal">true</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br><span class="line">RandomizedSet.prototype.remove = <span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span>(<span class="params">val</span>)</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="title">if</span>(<span class="params">!<span class="built_in">this</span>.map.has(val)</span>)</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="literal">false</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">const</span> index=<span class="built_in">this</span>.map.get(val);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> (index === <span class="built_in">this</span>.values.length-<span class="number">1</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">this</span>.values.pop();</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">this</span>.map.delete(val);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;<span class="keyword">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">const</span> lastValue = <span class="built_in">this</span>.values.pop();</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">this</span>.values[index] = lastValue;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">this</span>.map.set(lastValue,index);</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">this</span>.map.delete(val);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="literal">true</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br><span class="line">RandomizedSet.prototype.getRandom = <span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span>(<span class="params">val</span>)</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">const</span> length = <span class="built_in">this</span>.values.length;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">const</span> random = <span class="built_in">Math</span>.floor(<span class="built_in">Math</span>.random() * length);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="built_in">this</span>.values[random];</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="例3"><a href="#例3" class="headerlink" title="例3"></a>例3</h1><h2 id="771-宝石与石头"><a href="#771-宝石与石头" class="headerlink" title="771.宝石与石头"></a>771.宝石与石头</h2><h2 id="题目地址-2"><a href="#题目地址-2" class="headerlink" title="题目地址"></a>题目地址</h2><p><a href="https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/jewels-and-stones/">https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/jewels-and-stones/</a></p><h2 id="题目描述-2"><a href="#题目描述-2" class="headerlink" title="题目描述"></a>题目描述</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"> 给定字符串J 代表石头中宝石的类型，和字符串 S代表你拥有的石头。 S 中每个字符代表了一种你拥有的石头的类型，你想知道你拥有的石头中有多少是宝石。</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">J 中的字母不重复，J 和 S中的所有字符都是字母。字母区分大小写，因此&quot;a&quot;和&quot;A&quot;是不同类型的石头。</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">示例 1:</span><br><span class="line">输入: J &#x3D; &quot;aA&quot;, S &#x3D; &quot;aAAbbbb&quot;</span><br><span class="line">输出: 3</span><br><span class="line">示例 2:</span><br><span class="line">输入: J &#x3D; &quot;z&quot;, S &#x3D; &quot;ZZ&quot;</span><br><span class="line">输出: 0</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="思路-2"><a href="#思路-2" class="headerlink" title="思路"></a>思路</h2><p>1、遍历字符串J，J中字符存入哈希表中。（J 中的字母不重复，且此题只需要存key值，所以使用Set集合。）</p><p>2、遍历字符串S，对于其中每一个字符，如果其在哈希表中，则是宝石。</p><h2 id="代码-2"><a href="#代码-2" class="headerlink" title="代码"></a>代码</h2><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">var</span> numJewelsInStones = <span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span> (<span class="params">J, S</span>) </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">const</span> jewlsSet = <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="built_in">Set</span> (J.split(<span class="string">&quot;&quot;</span>));</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">//还可以通过循环添加到set中</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">//J.split(&quot;&quot;).forEach(val =&gt; jewlsSet.add(val));</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> S.split(<span class="string">&quot;&quot;</span>).reduce(<span class="function">(<span class="params">prev,val</span>) =&gt;</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> prev + jewlsSet.has(val);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;,<span class="number">0</span>);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="复杂度分析-1"><a href="#复杂度分析-1" class="headerlink" title="复杂度分析"></a>复杂度分析</h2><p>时间复杂度：O(m+n),其中m是字符串J的长度，n是字符串S的长度。<br>空间复杂度：O(m),其中m是是字符串J的长度。</p><h1 id="参考引用"><a href="#参考引用" class="headerlink" title="参考引用"></a>参考引用</h1><p><a href="http://www.conardli.top/docs/dataStructure/%E6%95%B0%E7%BB%84/%E4%B8%A4%E6%95%B0%E4%B9%8B%E5%92%8C.html">http://www.conardli.top/docs/dataStructure/%E6%95%B0%E7%BB%84/%E4%B8%A4%E6%95%B0%E4%B9%8B%E5%92%8C.html</a></p><p><a href="https://leetcode-solution-leetcode-pp.gitbook.io/leetcode-solution/medium/380.insert-delete-getrandom-o1">https://leetcode-solution-leetcode-pp.gitbook.io/leetcode-solution/medium/380.insert-delete-getrandom-o1</a></p>]]></content>
    
    
    <summary type="html">&lt;h1 id=&quot;哈希表-Hash&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#哈希表-Hash&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;哈希表(Hash)&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;哈希表(Hash)&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;哈希表&lt;/strong&gt;：是根据关键字而直接进行访问的数据结构。也就是说，哈希表建立了关键字和存储地址之间的一种直接映射关系。  &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;哈希的基本原理&lt;/strong&gt;：是将给定的键值转换为偏移地址来检索记录。&lt;br&gt;键转换为地址是通过一种关系(公式)来完成的，这就是哈希（散列）函数。Hash(key)=Addr。（这里的地址可以是数组下标、索引。或内存地址等。） &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;缺点&lt;/strong&gt;：两个不同的关键字，由于哈希函数值相同，因而被映射到同一表位置上。该现象称为冲突。发生冲突的两个关键字称为该哈希函数的同义词。&lt;/p&gt;</summary>
    
    
    
